Package civitas.celestis.ui.component

Interface UIComponent

public interface UIComponent
A UI component. Components can be added to a frame.

  • Method Details

    • render

      void render(@Nonnull RichImage image)
      Renders this component to the output image. The provided image is a raw reference to the frame's image.
      Parameters:
      image - The output image

    • getZ

      default int getZ()
      Returns the Z index of this component. Components with a higher Z index will be rendered last, thus taking priority.
      Returns:
      The Z index of this component
